    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[CreatedAt], [m].[InstalledDate], [m].[IsDeleted], [m].[Serial], [m].[Type], [m].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [Meters] AS [m]
    WHERE [m].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [m0] ON [c].[MeterId] = [m0].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[id], [c0].[address], [c0].[CreatedAt], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[name], [c0].[national_id], [c0].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [customers] AS [c0]
